  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b89\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bc8 - \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb9\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Reports that the International Monetary Fund and Japan will not help Sri Lanka are untrue - Minister Harin",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Reports that the International Monetary Fund and Japan will not provide any aid to Sri Lanka are untrue.",
        "The Board of Directors of the International Monetary Fund will also announce assistance to Sri Lanka only after we have submitted plans for debt restructuring and debt repayment.",
        "This is what the staff level team of the International Monetary Fund who stayed in Sri Lanka for the last 10 days said, said Tourism Minister Harin Fernando.",
        "He stated this at a press conference held on Friday (01) in Colombo, further mentioning,",
        "Reports in the media that the International Monetary Fund and Japan have announced that they will not help Sri Lanka are untrue.",
        "The International Monetary Fund has said that if the country does not break even, the next steps can be taken based on the decisions taken at the staff level.",
        "The Board of Directors of the International Monetary Fund will announce the final decision in this regard only after presenting a stable program on how we will repay the debts.",
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has taken steps to seek the help of two world-renowned companies, Lazard and Gilbert and Chance, to get support on how to prepare loan repayment plans.",
        "Only after the loan repayment program is clarified by these institutions, the IMF will announce how it will extend the loan to Sri Lanka.",
        "Similarly, fake news has been published that the ambassador of Japan has refused to help the country. These are actions taken in the hope of exacerbating the crisis in the country.",
        "Ranil Wickramasinghe accepted the challenge when no one else accepted the responsibility of solving the crises. It is irresponsible to raise slogans against him for that.",
        "Demonstrations should be carried out in the country. However, the opposition is pretending to be protesting to intensify the crisis. The country cannot be won through such activities. He said that protests cannot be won."
      ],
